item.title: The Father Wound (Guest: Jordan L. Jones & Ptosha Storey)
item.description:
In this powerful and heartfelt episode of Dear Future Wifey, we sit down with the incredibly talented mother-son duo, Ptosha Storey and Jordan L. Jones. From navigating Hollywood to building strong family bonds, they share raw, unfiltered wisdom on love, faith, healing, and legacy.

Ptosha, known for her captivating performances, opens up about motherhood, relationships, and trusting God’s plan after divorcing Jordan’s father, who is also in the acting industry...
